Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.00,0:00:06.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裏不會有任何人來打擾我們
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.73,0:00:07.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要上咯！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.53,0:00:17.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎喲哎喲！妳怎麽了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.64,0:00:23.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,餓狼嗎？自那之後我可真是太想見妳了！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.42,0:00:27.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我勸妳最好趕緊逃跑 虎心王
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.57,0:00:37.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這太讓我興奮了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.99,0:00:42.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以柔克剛是妳的絕技吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.27,0:00:48.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經…看透妳的伎倆了！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.73,0:01:04.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去死吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.56,0:01:05.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露妮！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.52,0:01:08.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滾開！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.35,0:01:17.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,軍師！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.17,0:01:21.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一個就是妳了 母狼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.50,0:01:39.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,百煉霸王與聖約女武神
