Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.69,0:02:12.50,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\yshad3}美麗永恒的光輝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.30,0:02:16.30,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\yshad3}吶喊吧　從此刻起
